{
  "stem": "1858.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 308.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did they did do to us?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was at times such as these that you sometimes begin feeling that you are indeed an untermensch, subhumans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So many times they succeeded in making us feel as an untermensch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Punishments during the roll call, such as beating or shaving your hair, was already an everyday occurrence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had almost no effect on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was what they did to us that mentally affected us was sometimes even worse than just beating.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this could happen any time, or many times we'd come from work and a girl would be called to barrack duty after working so hard all day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if the girl was too weak, or too sick, another girl who was not much stronger would go and do it for her.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barrack duty, like go and wash the toilets or the washrooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Toilets, our toilets were-- it was on a hill on the side of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a little building with a board and holes in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no toilet such as we're thinking toilets that you flush it or you sit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you had to wash that or washroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our washroom was also a long hall with like a long sink and just a pipe going across with water dipping out of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the washroom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or washing floors, or sweeping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If a girl would be called to barrack duty such as that, and if she was too weak, and, as I said, another girl would go and do it for her, so as to cover up that she's unable, that she's too sick, to give her time to perhaps let her live.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I cannot describe to you how helpful-- how we covered up for each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
